      We tested 57 public strategies. Most failed. This report shows which ones survived — and exactly why the rest died.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="#buy" style="display:inline-block;padding:0.75rem 2rem;background:var(--color-text);color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;font-size:1rem;font-weight:500;">Buy Report — $9</a>
